  "title": "Admin & Sales Support Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are looking for a motivated Admin &amp; Sales Support Executive to assist our sales and after-sales team with administrative, invoicing, and customer-related tasks. This is an ideal role for someone who is organized, detail-oriented.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities: </strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Provide administrative and clerical support to the sales and after-sales team</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Assist the sales team in handing customer general enquiries, generating accurate quotations and managing follow-ups on outstanding orders.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Assist the after-sales team in maintaining and follow-up service contract and renewal.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Issue Delivery Order, invoices, and follow up on outstanding payments</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Maintain office consumables inventory &amp; order supplies when necessary</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Assist with call, general office administration and ad-hoc duties</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Proficiency in English. </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Minimum GCE O/N Level or equivalent; fresh graduates are welcome</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Strong attention to detail and basic MS Office or software knowledge</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Knowledge in Microsoft Office (Word &amp; Excel)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Good communication and time management skills</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Able to work independently and as part of a team</p>",
